short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly fill in links from browser history.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
1. Open/close search window right-click or keyboard shortcut (defaults to `Ctrl+Shift+X`).
2. Search through history. Results continuously update as you type.
3. Use keyboard arrows to select a result.
4. URL is inserted into last text box you selected.
